Class ResultRequirement

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.usz.c3pro.c3_pro_android_framework.questionnaire.logic.ResultRequirement

    public class ResultRequirement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class implements the logic of Questionnaire.QuestionnaireItemEnableWhenComponents. For every Questionnaire.QuestionnaireItemEnableWhenComponent of an item, a ResultRequirement should be added to the according Steps of the item and its child items.
